{"tid":706803,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"QB House 飛髪🙉","createTime":"2018-06-18T07:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T11:48:48.000Z","uid":27388,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1dff5a9b17dd124b78d5bcd812234b46b66145","tid":706803,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"依家出去飛個髪普普通都收我150元<br />\n<br />\n剪左成世人頭，都未試過去呢d地方剪<br />\n<br />\n真心話：只要把頭髮整理好即可，我唔需要洗兩次頭，也不需要按摩頭，都唔需要問我要飲d咩，我最希望快一d剪完頭髮<br />\n<br />\n今日第一次試完10分快剪...同150元的冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4ac07a76c81016226afcfee33672c387bb8d2d","tid":706803,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"以後唔好返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c9ebcba5e80c66e307f0dba4becba599572ded","tid":706803,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"我都去qb剪 平靚正"},{"pid":"f30228353a1b2b265d73665124dc7b36d68cefa7","tid":706803,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d4ac07a76c81016226afcfee33672c387bb8d2d","tid":706803,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"以後唔好返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"正常街鋪我剪個頭都起碼最少90分鐘...仲要等"},{"pid":"8052440f715f28eab81bb1af58391bac1c58c83e","tid":706803,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f30228353a1b2b265d73665124dc7b36d68cefa7","tid":706803,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d4ac07a76c81016226afcfee33672c387bb8d2d","tid":706803,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"以後唔好返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"正常街鋪我剪個頭都起碼最少90分鐘...仲要等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"唔洗講咁多<br />\n用行動証明比我睇"},{"pid":"c0632121f5413b6e262de0340977cf7bb3a0aa52","tid":706803,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"metoo<br />\n<br />\n剪左$150-180好多年<br />\n<br />\n終於試下$50/60 果d 速剪<br />\n<br />\n唔係大修，純粹剪短偷薄，好滿意"},{"pid":"0f6370fc3d7fb9be6fb21ddea93ad6718ba56739","tid":706803,"uid":119361,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"我又係, 十幾年都同一間由幾十加到百六七<br />\n<br />\n今年過年前見佢冇開就去左 QB ， 60 搞掂..。以後去到講 6mm 同邊個位想點就剪返個型。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得修下剪返短用 QB 就ok, 比咁既價錢都預左係咁上下 services<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda31f7b01aa8a35e0db9c208db8fb2d4ccafdbb","tid":706803,"uid":115910,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:15:01.000Z","msg":"其實一個男仔普通髮型去速剪就得<br />\n<br />\n咩剪碎偷薄個個都咁剪，你去幾舊水果啲佢咪懶細心同你修的水磨時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712923ed3fed73d0ab700331d1db8f7ca03b2aaa","tid":706803,"uid":12001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:23:59.000Z","msg":"有個油頭同事我以為佢去開barber shop<br />\n點知佢同我講佢都係去qb house<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0eae9a849d26bac5c9a6c34d9f863835494a07","tid":706803,"uid":27388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"剪出黎樣唔係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f8e12234005eba22179b0a13b111ab52474740","tid":706803,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:03:55.000Z","msg":"不嬲都去速剪 慳好多時間<br />\n但係一到假期就好多人排 等得黎仲慢過去salon洗剪吹"},{"pid":"8c382e3513926dac756d6b7cf392345245457cc5","tid":706803,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:0